*[[L<U+00E4>ngloh]]
*[[Moos]]
*[[Ortlfing]]
*[[Stra<U+00DF>]]
*[[Wengen]]
|}

==Note==
There is a municipality in the same district named [[Bergheim (Bavaria)|Bergheim]].

